            sum += lst[i] * lst[i] * lst[i]
        else:
            sum += lst[i] * lst[i] * lst[i] * lst[i]
    return sum

    """
    sum = 0
    for i in range(len(lst)):
        if i % 3 == 0:
            sum += lst[i] * lst[i]
        elif i % 4 == 0:
            sum += lst[i] * lst[i] * lst[i]
        else:
            sum += lst[i] * lst[i] * lst[i] * lst[i]
    return sum
